Manajemen Proses dan Memori	
- Monitoring proses (ps, top, htop)
- Menjalankan dan mengelola proses (jobs, fg, bg, nohup, kill, nice, renice)
- Manajemen memori dan swap (free, vmstat, swapon, swapoff)

#Prompt Terminal
free -sh
cat /proc/meminfo
cat /proc/cpuinfo
lscpu
swapon --summary
vmstat -s
ps aux --sort=-%mem|head
whoami
chmod --version
sudo reboot
sudo shutdown -h how + 10
sudo shutdown -cl
sudo shutdown -r now
